response.overview: Join the Bubble Guppies in the most fin-tastic fairy tales of all! First, a with turns Bubble Puppy into a frog and Molly and Gil need to team up with this fairytale friends to undo her mean green spell! Next, Hansel and Gretel must get Bubble Puppy and Bubble Kitty home safe to their Furry Godmother. Finally, we meet Alison in a place called Wonderland and need to stop the Queen of Hearts from banning Friendship Day across the land!
response.title: Bubble Guppies: Fin-tastic Fairy Tales!
